Class SimpleFloat3

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Float3

    public class SimpleFloat3
extends java.lang.Object
implements Float3
    A simple 3-D array of floats. Implements the generic interface Float3 using a straightforward Java 3-D array of floats.
